{"tid":166090,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"Metal求推介","createTime":"2017-03-22T00:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T10:35:39.000Z","uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0dfb52514afa87a992b486f9e5ff127d165ee505","tid":166090,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:06:07.000Z","msg":"主要對gothic, doom, symphonic, progressive同power metal有興趣<br />\n特別鍾意有一大段純音樂得少量人聲嘅歌<br />\n最鍾意有violin solo嘅<br />\n鍾意男聲 越佬越好<br />\n黑金嗰啲我未handle到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我喜歡嘅band有我自己，novembers doom，stratovarius，paradise lost，saturnus，lake of tears，katatonia<br />\n求推介相似嘅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n拋磚<br />\n<br />\nTwilight Innocence - Novembers Doom<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AFgkLLQ-r2Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAFgkLLQ-r2Y&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8c2f2555\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AFgkLLQ-r2Y</a><br />\n<br />\nDescending - Saturnus<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6Y8dAIqdw2o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6Y8dAIqdw2o&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0c0ea7ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6Y8dAIqdw2o</a><br />\n<br />\nTo Blossom Blue - Lake of Tears<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wEcEjNsn1Io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwEcEjNsn1Io&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6dc5fe1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wEcEjNsn1Io</a><br />\n<br />\nMy Wine in Silence - My Dying Bride<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/moHl3LWxTnU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmoHl3LWxTnU&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e7eab9c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/moHl3LWxTnU</a>"},{"pid":"7108e0d10ab0c5bf9ea84ec1cb18357e4508de57","tid":166090,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:13:44.000Z","msg":"想聽黎灰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  輕輕一推<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-F1D_X6hfmc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-F1D_X6hfmc&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a1f3c824\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-F1D_X6hfmc</a><br />\nAll Alone - Saturnus<br />\n<br />\nI'm standing here<br />\nWatcing the clouds float by<br />\nWondering why the pain never deserted me<br />\nThe sadness, sorrow, bewilderness that never left<br />\n...the moments of joy I never kept<br />\n<br />\nI'm flying away<br />\n<br />\nHolding hands with myself<br />\nSharing life with myself<br />\nReaping the loneliness I've sown<br />\nIn these fields I've always grown<br />\nDigging the blackness from my mind<br />\nI will die all alone"},{"pid":"8666c155c3b10f339f4b36e7297315261f43ab3f","tid":166090,"uid":31172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:46:31.000Z","msg":"primordial<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bea28e2988218fbfef7808d8a3f8b07ac9dcdd4","tid":166090,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T01:03:33.000Z","msg":"舊啲嘅 black veil brides"},{"pid":"044664dacea40e1cbad2805895bd1426ba202f15","tid":166090,"uid":26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T01:10:09.000Z","msg":"日本 Galneryus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72650725a847f3eceda21cccdc340288e348895c","tid":166090,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"唔該曬幾位巴打<br />\nPish"},{"pid":"162bb915851f051ef272d19b8088106449381037","tid":166090,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"Swallow the sun<br />\n<br />\nInsomnium 👈 5月黎香港<img src=\"/assets/fac